ets (A Thousand Regrets)","Artist":"Christian Bérard","Date":"1947","Medium":"One from the supplementary suite of nineteen collotype and pochoir reproductions of an illustrated book with fifty-five collotype and pochoir reproductions","CreditLine":"The Louis E. Stern Collection","URL":"https://www.moma.org/collection/works/416440","ImageURL":"https://www.moma.org/media/W1siZiIsIjE3MTY1MCJdLFsicCIsImNvbnZlcnQiLCItcmVzaXplIDEwMjR4MTAyNFx1MDAzZSJdXQ.jpg?sha=1fd2614abe728e20"},{"ObjectID":423314,"Title":"The opposite of looking is not invisibility. The opposite of yellow is not gold","Artist":"Hương Ngô, Hồng-An Trương","Date":"2016","Medium":"Installation with inkjet and laser cut prints","CreditLine":"Fund for the Twenty-First Century","URL":"https://www.moma.org/collection/works/423314","ImageURL":"https://www.moma.org/media/W1siZiIsIjQyNzUyMiJdLFsicCIsImNvbnZlcnQiLCItcmVzaXplIDEwMjR4MTAyNFx1MDAzZSJdXQ.jpg?sha=0c512ebda37a8a68"},{"ObjectID":424296,"Title":"Horizontal 6 (Villages of  Ericó) from the series Marcados","Artist":"Claudia Andujar","Date":"1981-83","Medium":"Gelatin silver print, printed 2006","CreditLine":"Acquired with support from the Committee on Photography Fund, the Latin American And Caribbean Fund and through the generosity of Alec Oxenford, and Ariel Sigal","URL":"https://www.moma.org/collection/works/424296","ImageURL":"https://www.moma.org/media/W1siZiIsIjUwNzY2NCJdLFsicCIsImNvbnZlcnQiLCItcmVzaXplIDEwMjR4MTAyNFx1MDAzZSJdXQ.jpg?sha=eae5bceadcf4c5b8"},{"ObjectID":467504,"Title":"Untitled from the portfolio Green Self Models","Artist":"Carroll Dunham","Date":"2021-22","Medium":"One from a portfolio of seven lithographs","CreditLine":"Acquired through the generosity of Mary M. and Sash A. Spencer","URL":"https://www.moma.org/collection/works/467504","ImageURL":"https://www.moma.org/media/W1siZiIsIjU2NjU1NyJdLFsicCIsImNvbnZlcnQiLCItcmVzaXplIDEwMjR4MTAyNFx1MDAzZSJdXQ.jpg?sha=e6b1c734b7a1f8b5"}]